<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MJ Pastelaria</title>

    <style> 
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        .center {
            max-width: 960px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0 2%;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgb(226, 43, 43);
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .banner {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .banner h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: rgb(226, 43, 43);
        }

        .banner p {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .botao {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: rgb(226, 43, 43);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="center">
            <div class="logo">MJ Pastelaria</div>

            <nav>
                <a href="#">Home</a>
                <a href="#">Sobre</a>
                <a href="#">Cardápio</a>
                <a href="#">Contato</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="banner">
        <h1>Os melhores pastéis da cidade!</h1>
        <p>Venha experimentar sabores incríveis feitos na hora</p>
        <a href="#" class="botao">Ver Cardápio</a>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
